members.name: SpeechSynthesisVoice.default
members.description: A Boolean indicating whether the voice is the default voice for the current app language (true), or not (false.)

members.name: SpeechSynthesisVoice.lang
members.description: Returns a BCP 47 language tag indicating the language of the voice.

members.name: SpeechSynthesisVoice.localService
members.description: A Boolean indicating whether the voice is supplied by a local speech synthesizer service (true), or a remote speech synthesizer service (false.)

members.name: SpeechSynthesisVoice.name
members.description: Returns a human-readable name that represents the voice.

members.name: SpeechSynthesisVoice.voiceURI
members.description: Returns the type of URI and location of the speech synthesis service for this voice.
